5.3 Prizes will be dispatched to the prize winners via the UK mail service unless otherwise stated in the applicable Specific Terms or if the prize is a cash prize. Prizes will be delivered to addresses within the UK only. If a prize winner’s contact details change, it is their responsibility to notify us. We will not be liable for any prizes which are lost, delayed, or damaged in the post for reasons beyond our control.
5.4 If the prize is a cash prize, the winner will be required to provide UK bank details to us within 7 days of our requesting these by contacting the winner. If the winner fails to provide this information within this time, we reserve the right to choose an alternative prize winner or not issue the prize at all.
