our website terms and conditions and any documents referred to in them, including without limitation our privacy policy (see twinkl.co.uk/legal);
extra terms which may add to, or replace some of, this contract. This may happen for security, legal, regulatory, or other reasonable reasons. We will contact you to let you know if we intend to do this by giving you one month’s notice. If you do not agree to these changes, you can end this contract at any time by giving notice under these terms and conditions in accordance with clause 5; and
specific terms which apply to certain Product Services. These are detailed on the relevant webpage for the Product Service as updated from time to time.
All of the documents in clause 1.5 form part of this contract as though set out in full here. If there is a conflict between the website terms and conditions and these terms and conditions, these terms and conditions will apply to that extent.
