Subscribing to a Product Service
Below, we set out how a legally binding contract between you and us is made.
You place an order to subscribe for the Product Service by clicking the ‘Subscribe Now’ button on the Product Service page, entering your details, and filling in and submitting your payment details. Please read and check your order carefully before submitting it. You will be able to correct any errors before submitting your order to us.
